<h2 id="goals">Goals</h2>

<h3 id="prepare-the-buffers-a1-e1">Prepare the buffers A1-E1</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Calculate the concentration of each component present in buffers A1-E1 using the concentration of each stock solution, the volume of each solution delivered, and the total volume of buffer created.</li>
</ul>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th style="text-align: center">Solution</th>
